name: Gigabyte H310M H 8th Gen Micro ATX Motherboard
description: Gigabyte H310M H 8th Gen Micro ATX Motherboard is compatible with Intel (Socket LGA1151) i3, i5 & i7 processor. This 8-Channel HD Audio with High Quality Audio Capacitor board has dual channel DDR4 maximum 32GB memory and it has the capability of Ultra-Fast SATA 6Gb/s connectors and USB 3.1 Gen 1 interface. If we consider the graphics of this Anti-Sulfur Resistors Design board supports Intel HD graphics having the maximum resolution of 4096x2160@30 Hz for HDMI and 1920x1200@60 Hz for D-Sub port. This High Quality Audio Capacitors and Audio board has 3 x PCIe slot, GIGABYTE Exclusive 8118 Gaming LAN with Bandwidth Management,  Smart Fan 5 features Multiple Temperature Sensors and Hybrid Fan Headers with FAN STOP and all new GIGABYTE™ APP Center which is simple and easy use.

name: Toshiba DT01ABA100V 1TB Surveillance Hard Drive
description: The Toshiba DT01ABA100V is a 1TB Surveillance Hard Drive that is suitable for video editing, set-top-box (STB), digital video recorders (DVR), and network video recorders (NVR) applications where large capacity, low power, and low acoustics are critical. It features a 3.5-inch, Low Profile Form Factor with up to 5,700 rpm speed. It comes with a SATA up to 6.0 Gbit/s interface. It has a max data transfer speed of 1443 Mbit/s. It has an average latency time of 5.27ms and a buffer size of 32 MiB. It is RoHS compatible. It comes with 2 years of warranty.

name: Colorful GeForce GTX1050Ti 4G-V 4GB GDDR5 Graphics Card

name: Transcend 230S 128GB 2.5 Inch SATA III SSD
description: Transcend TS1TSSD230S SSD uses the latest 3D NAND technology that features vertical, stacked expansion of storage cells. In this SSD, It has SATA III 6Gb/s interface, 560 MB/s maximum read sequential, 380 MB/s maximum write sequential with 1,000,000 hour(s) MTBF. This SSD Operating Temperature about 0°C (32°F) ~ 70°C (158°F). The System Requirement for this SSD are Microsoft Windows 7, Microsoft Windows 8, Microsoft Windows 10, Linux Kernel 2.6.31 or later. In this SSD TRIM & NCQ Command, S.M.A.R.T., DDR3 DRAM Cache, Advanced Garbage Collection, DevSleep Mode, RAID Engine and LDPC Coding technologies are used. It balso provides 03 years of warranty. By using high-quality flash memory and enhanced firmware algorithms, the SSD230S delivers greater performance and reliability. It comes with 5 years warranty.

name: Antec VP650 Plus 650W Non Modular Power Supply
description: The new generation of VP650 PLUS is crafted for quality, performance and incredible value. This entry-level solution is rated from 500W to 650W, saving energy through its high efficiency of up to 85% efficient and is 80 PLUS Standard certified. Delivering up to 85% efficiency, the VP PLUS series utilizes active PFC, and provides efficiency during max and low loads—living up to the performance standards that we are known for. We stand by the quality and safety of the VP PLUS Power Supplies, offering 3-year parts and labor warranty and unlimited access to our incomparable technical support and customer service. The 120 mm Silent Fan is ideal for quiet computing and is designed for longer life, guaranteeing hours of operation. Features a Thermal Manager, an advanced low voltage fan control for optimal heat & noise management and will allow your PSU to stay at an optimal temperature.

name: AMD Ryzen Boxed Cooling Fan Original
description: AMD Ryzen Boxed Cooling Fans are the Original CPU coolers usually offered with an AMD Ryzen series of processors. This CPU supports the AMD Ryzen family of CPUs. Namely Ryzen 3, Ryzen 5, Ryzen 7, and Ryzen 9. The supported Socket of this cooler is AM4. This cooler has a 90 mm Fan and the size is 90x90x25mm. The CPU fan utilizes a Fluid Bearing. The Fan Life is 100000 hrs and the cooler's Power Interface is a 4pin PWM connector as a Power Interface. it is compatible with any AM4 Socket Compatible Processor. The Heatsink is a specialized AMD CPU Heatsink made with Aluminum. The Aluminium heatsink and 4pin power connector ensure maximum efficiency.
